dct_title_s: Pascaerte van Nova Hispania, Chili, Peru, en Guatimala
dct_description_sm: From : De Zee-atlas ofte water-wereld ... T'Amsterdam, by Pieter Goos... 1666. Nautical chart showing the coastline of Central America, Peru, and Chile. Oriented with north towards left.
dct_publisher_sm: t'Amsterdam : by Pieter Goos, op't Waater inde Verguelde Zeespiegel, Ao. 1666.
